#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a module for scheduling programs to run in the background. It is a "
"graphical user interface to <command>cron</command>, the &UNIX; system "
"scheduler."
msgstr ""
"本模块用来调度在后台运行的程序。它是<command>cron</command>（&UNIX;系统调度"
"器）的一个图形用户界面。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Don't forget to tell your system to start the <filename>crond</filename> "
"cron daemon first, or the settings in this module will not work."
msgstr ""
"不要忘记先让系统启动<filename>crond</filename>即 cron 守护进程，否则本模块的"
"设置将不会起作用。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start Up"
msgstr "启动界面"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start this module you will see a summarized view of existing "
"scheduled tasks and associated environment variables. If you are running as "
"the root user, you will see these items for all users on the computer as "
"well as the system scheduled tasks."
msgstr ""
"当您启动该模块后，您将可以看到一个显示已有的计划任务和与其相关联的环境变量的"
"简要界面。如果您以 root 用户身份启动，您可以看到计算机上所有用户以及系统的计"
"划任务。"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>start up</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>启动界面</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>start up</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>启动界面</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduled Tasks"
msgstr "计划任务"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scheduled tasks appear under a <guilabel>Tasks</guilabel> list. For each "
"scheduled task, the following items are displayed:"
msgstr ""
"计划任务在<guilabel>任务</guilabel>列表中显示。对每一个计划任务，下列项目将会"
"显示："

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduling"
msgstr "计划"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this column either \"@reboot\" for task schedules at boot or the crontab "
"entry is displayed."
msgstr ""
"该列可能显示“@reboot”字段以表示该任务在启动时进行，或是显示对应的 crontab 记"
"录。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:100 index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command"
msgstr "命令"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Program file and parameters."
msgstr "程序文件及其参数。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:104 index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status"
msgstr "状态"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105 index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabled or Disabled."
msgstr "已启用或已禁用。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "A description for the task, such as its purpose."
msgstr "对任务的描述，比如该任务的目的。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduling Details"
msgstr "计划细节"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Natural language description of scheduled task."
msgstr "计划任务的自然语言描述。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment Variables"
msgstr "环境变量"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Environment variables appear in the <guilabel>Environment Variables</"
"guilabel> list. For each environment variable, the following are displayed:"
msgstr ""
"环境变量显示在<guilabel>环境变量</guilabel>列表中。对每个环境变量，下列项目将"
"会显示："

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:130 index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variable"
msgstr "变量"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variable name."
msgstr "变量名称。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:134 index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Value"
msgstr "值"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variable value."
msgstr "变量的值。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:142 index.docbook:180 index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comment"
msgstr "注释"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Natural language description of variable."
msgstr "变量的自然语言描述。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Environment variables appearing here will override any existing environment "
"variable for all scheduled tasks."
msgstr "此处显示的环境变量将会覆盖所有计划任务任何先前已有的环境变量。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Scheduled Tasks"
msgstr "添加计划任务"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new scheduled task, click the <guibutton>New Task...</guibutton> "
"button. Alternatively, you can select this action from the "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button context menu."
msgstr ""
"要创建新计划任务，点击<guibutton>新建任务...</guibutton>按钮。除此之外，您还"
"可以从鼠标<mousebutton>右键</mousebutton>上下文菜单中选择该操作。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Task Dialog"
msgstr "任务编辑对话框"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Edit Task</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr "<guilabel>编辑任务</guilabel>对话框。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Edit Task</guilabel> dialog"
msgstr "<guilabel>编辑任务</guilabel>对话框"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the name of the program. You can specify either a relative path or "
"absolute path. If you want to look up the program, click <guiicon>Browse</"
"guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"输入程序名称。您可以使用绝对路径或者相对路径。如果您需要寻找某个程序，请点击"
"<guiicon>浏览</guiicon>图标。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter a description of the task to schedule."
msgstr "输入计划任务的描述。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable this task"
msgstr "启用此任务"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "To enable or disable the task, select or de-select this button."
msgstr "要启用或者禁用任务，请选中或者取消选中该项。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run at system boot-up"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this button to run the task at system boot-up."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run every day"
msgstr "每天运行"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you want to schedule the task to run daily, select this button."
msgstr "如果您想让该任务每天运行，请选中该项。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Months"
msgstr "月份"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the months during which the task is to be scheduled."
msgstr "选择该任务计划运行的月份。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Days of Month"
msgstr "日 (按月选择)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the days of the month on which the task is to be scheduled."
msgstr "选择要计划任务的月份中的日期。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Days of Week"
msgstr "日 (按周选择)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the days of the week on which the task is to be scheduled."
msgstr "选择该任务计划运行的星期中的日子。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hours"
msgstr "小时"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the hours on which the task is to be scheduled."
msgstr "选择该任务计划运行的小时数。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minutes"
msgstr "分钟"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the minute at which the task is to be scheduled. <command>cron</"
"command> does not support scheduling tasks at smaller than one minute "
"intervals."
msgstr ""
"选择该任务计划运行的分钟数。<command>cron</command>不支持设置小于一分钟的计划"
"任务时间间隔。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:235 index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>OK</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>确定</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completes the creation of this task."
msgstr "完成任务的创建。"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:240 index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancels the creation of this task."
msgstr "取消任务的创建。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select both days of the month, and days of the week, the task will "
"run when either condition is met. For instance, if you select the 1st and "
"15th, and select Sunday, the program will be run every 1st and 15th of the "
"selected months (regardless of day of week) as well as every Sunday of the "
"selected months (regardless of day of the month)."
msgstr ""
"如果您既选择了一月中的天数，又选择了一周中的天数，任务在其中任何一个条件满足"
"时都会运行。例如，如果您选择了每月的第一天和第十五天，又选择了星期日，则程序"
"会在每个选定月份的第一天和第十五天运行（无论那天是星期几），也会在选定月份的"
"每个星期日运行（无论那天是每月的第几天）。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scheduled task is not actually set up until the <filename>crontab</"
"filename> has been saved."
msgstr "所计划的任务不会实际生效，直到<filename>crontab</filename>得到保存。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Scheduled Tasks"
msgstr "管理任务计划"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with creating new tasks, changes to tasks will not actually be made until "
"the <filename>crontab</filename> is saved."
msgstr ""
"对于创建新任务，对任务的修改不会实际生效，直到<filename>crontab</filename>得"
"到保存。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the buttons at the right of the task list to modify, delete, print or "
"run a selected task now. You reach all these actions from the context menu "
"as well. Additionally the context menu provides actions to cut, copy and "
"paste tasks."
msgstr ""
"使用任务列表右侧的按钮来修改、删除、打印或者直接运行选中的任务。您也可以从右"
"键菜单中选择这些操作。另外，右键菜单中也提供了诸如剪切、复制和粘贴任务的操"
"作。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Environment Variables"
msgstr "添加环境变量"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new environment variable, click the <guibutton>New Variable...</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr "如需创建一个新的环境变量，点击<guibutton>新建变量...</guibutton>按钮。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can use the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button "
"menu to choose this action."
msgstr ""
"另外，您也可以使用鼠标<mousebutton>右键</mousebutton>按钮的菜单来选择这个操"
"作。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Variable dialog"
msgstr "变量编辑对话框"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo><guilabel>Edit Variable</guilabel> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo><guilabel>编辑变量</guilabel>对话框。</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase><guilabel>Edit Variable</guilabel> dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase><guilabel>编辑变量</guilabel>对话框。</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the environment variable name. You can use the drop down list box to "
"select from the most common environment variables used by scheduled tasks. "
"Those include:"
msgstr ""
"输入环境变量名。您可以使用下拉列表按钮选择计划任务最常用的环境变量。它们包"
"括："

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "HOME"
msgstr "HOME"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "To be used instead of the default user's home folder."
msgstr "用于替代默认用户的家目录。"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "MAILTO"
msgstr "MAILTO"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To send email output to an email address other than the user's default email "
"address."
msgstr "用于向指定的邮件地址发出电子邮件，而不使用用户默认的电子邮件地址。"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "PATH"
msgstr "PATH"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "To be used to search folders for program files."
msgstr "用于指定搜索程序的文件夹。"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "SHELL"
msgstr "SHELL"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "To be used instead of the user's default value."
msgstr "用于替代用户的默认值。"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "LD_CONFIG_PATH"
msgstr "LD_CONFIG_PATH"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location of dynamic libraries. This allows cron jobs to execute "
"applications which have libraries they need to run installed outside the "
"system library path."
msgstr ""
"指定动态链接库的位置。它使得 cron 任务能够运行那些所使用的动态链接库在系统库"
"路径之外的应用程序。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the environment variable value."
msgstr "输入环境变量值。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter a description for the environment variable, such as its purpose."
msgstr "输入环境变量的描述信息，例如其目的。"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable this variable"
msgstr "启用此变量"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "To enable or disable the variable, select or de-select this button."
msgstr "要启用或者禁用变量，请选中或者取消选中该项。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completes the setting of this variable."
msgstr "完成该变量的设置。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancels the setting of this variable."
msgstr "取消该变量的设置。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The environment variable is not actually set up until the <filename>crontab</"
"filename> has been saved."
msgstr ""
"所设置的环境变量不会实际生效，直到<filename>crontab</filename>得到保存。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Environment Variables"
msgstr "管理环境变量"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with creating new variables, changes to variables will not actually be "
"made until the <filename>crontab</filename> is saved."
msgstr ""
"对于创建新变量，其变量的修改不会实际生效，直到<filename>crontab</filename>得"
"到保存。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the buttons at the right of the variable list to modify or delete a "
"selected variable. You reach all these actions from the context menu as "
"well. Additionally the context menu provides actions to cut, copy and paste "
"variables."
msgstr ""
"使用任务列表右侧的按钮来修改或删除选中的变量。您也可以从右键菜单中选择这些操"
"作。另外，右键菜单中也提供了诸如剪切、复制和粘贴变量的操作。"
